high_descs: Go right into the kitchen and turn left to face the counter.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Go left and then left again and face the counter with the lettuce on it.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and face the microwave.
Put the knife down in front of the microwave.
Turn around and face the counter behind with the lettuce on it.
Pick the lettuce up from the counter.
Go left and then turn right to face the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the lettuce up again.
Turn around and face the microwave.
Put the lettuce down in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put clean lettuce on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward to the stove, turn left, move forward to the counter.
Pick up the knife.
Turn left, move forward to just before the fridge, turn left, move forward to the counter.
Slice the head of lettuce.
Turn around, move forward to the microwave.
Put the knife on the stovetop in front of the microwave.
Turn around, move to the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left, move to alongside the sink, turn right.
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink, turn on the faucet for 3 seconds, turn off the faucet, pick up the slice of lettuce.
Turn right, move forward to alongside the lettuce on the counter, turn right, move forward to the microwave.
Place the slice of lettuce on the stovetop near the knife.
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce and put a slice of lettuce near the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter in the corner of the room
Grab that knife that is on the counter
Turn around and head to the counter in the opposite corner
Cut the lettuce into slices
Turn around and head to the microwave
Put the knife on the black table
Turn around and go to the counter with the lettuce
Pick up a slice of lettuce
Turn left and go to the sink
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then grab it
Turn around and go to the microwave
Put the lettuce on the black table
anns.task_desc: Putting sliced lettuce on the black table
